{"id":"cdb2bd49-054b-49eb-b0ef-24b527f14132","name":"Dragon Ball Super: Super Hero Action Figure S.H. Figuarts Orange Piccolo 18cm","slug":"dragon-ball-super:-super-hero-action-fig","description":"<p><b>Dragon Ball Super: Super Hero </b>Action Figure of <b>Orange Piccolo </b>in <b>S.H. Figuarts </b>collection, size approx.18cm. <b>Official product</b> by <strong>Tamashii Nations</strong>.</p>\n<p>Orange Piccolo from the movie Dragon Ball Super: SUPER HERO is now available from S.H.Figuarts!</p>\n<p>The image from the movie is reproduced to the last detail, like the figure’s balance of the head and body, the buffed up muscles, and the creased look of the martial arts uniform! Three types of facial expression parts are included as accessories, including the face shouting when Piccolo confronts Cell Max.</p>\n<p>Similarly to S.H.Figuarts Son Gohan Beast (sold separately), flexible parts are used for the martial arts uniform to achieve both appearance and mobility! </p>\n<p>This product is not a toy or product for children. It is a collectors item intended for adults only.</p>","metaTitle":null,"metaDescription":null,"model":null,"releaseDate":null,"image":null,"condition":null,"edition":null,"rarity":null,"features":null,"specifications":null,"createdAt":"2025-03-23T01:54:26.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-03-23T11:18:49.748Z","barcode":"4573102650429","deletedAt":null,"brandId":"7a967784-dc85-42fa-b79e-9628380428ae","franchiseId":null,"seriesId":null,"lineId":null,"categories":[{"productId":"cdb2bd49-054b-49eb-b0ef-24b527f14132","categoryId":"3ddb5c14-b646-4420-b55e-71845478f916","category":{"id":"3ddb5c14-b646-4420-b55e-71845478f916","name":"Collectibles","slug":"collectibles","description":"","image":null,"parentId":null,"createdAt":"2025-03-23T00:41:53.192Z","updatedAt":"2025-03-23T00:41:53.192Z","deletedAt":null}}],"retailerPrices":[{"id":"20d8bfb2-22a4-46a9-bb52-9353952d4a00","productId":"cdb2bd49-054b-49eb-b0ef-24b527f14132","retailerId":"01c5d85f-8559-486d-b0a9-3bd97e4